We also have `hT : (ѕЗ вЖТ ќЊ) вИЙ T.theory`. So we need to show that `this` and `hT` are contradictory. The only way to do this is if `(ќУ.conj вЛП ѕЖ)` implies `ѕЗ вЖТ ќЊ`, which would mean `(ѕЗ вЖТ ќЊ) вИИ T.theory`, contradicting `hT`.

So we need to show `(ќУ.conj вЛП ѕЖ) вЖТ (ѕЗ вЖТ ќЊ)`. If we can establish this, then `this` would imply `hT` is false, giving us the contradiction.

